reagent-name-phenol-formaldehyde = Phenol-Formaldehyde resin
reagent-desc-phenol-formaldehyde = Phenol-Formaldehyde Resin is a common molding polymer used in production of many small parts. It has great stress capacity and proven itself over many decades.
